videos.headline: Knight gets NC State on the board
videos.description: Zonovan Knight bursts through the hole and scores the nine-yard touchdown putting NC State up 7-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Knight gets NC State on the board) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: After 45 yard gain, NC State's McKay powers into end zone for TD
videos.description: After Ricky Person Jr. gains 45 yards, quarterback Matthew McKay pushes his way into the end zone giving the Wolfpack a 17-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (After 45 yard gain, NC State's McKay powers into end zone for TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: NC State's McKay scores 2nd rushing TD of the day
videos.description: NC State quarterback Matthew McKay finds the end zone from 21 yards out giving him two rushing touchdowns for the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (NC State's McKay scores 2nd rushing TD of the day) 2019/08/31
